<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= mode === 'create' ? '新增学生' : '编辑学生' %> - 学生信息管理系统</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="app-page">
  <div class="app-shell">
    <%- include('partials/sidebar', {
      activePage: 'studentForm',
      user: typeof user !== 'undefined' ? user : null,
      sidebarStats: typeof sidebarStats !== 'undefined' ? sidebarStats : null
    }) %>

    <div class="app-content">
  <header class="subpage-topbar">
    <div class="subpage-topbar-inner">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-1">Student Hub</p>
        <h1 class="page-title mb-0"><%= mode === 'create' ? '新增学生' : '编辑学生' %></h1>
      </div>
      <a href="/students" class="btn btn-outline-light">返回列表</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="subpage-main">
    <section class="form-layout">
      <article class="panel form-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <div>
            <p class="section-kicker">Profile</p>
            <h3>档案信息</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="<%= formAction %>" method="POST" class="row g-3">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label" for="student_no">学号</label>
            <input id="student_no" type="text" name="student_no" class="form-control" value="<%= student.student_no || '' %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label" for="name">姓名</label>
            <input id="name" type="text" name="name" class="form-control" value="<%= student.name || '' %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label" for="gender">性别</label>
            <select id="gender" name="gender" class="form-select">
              <option value="男" <%= student.gender === '男' ? 'selected' : '' %>>男</option>
              <option value="女" <%= student.gender === '女' ? 'selected' : '' %>>女</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label class="form-label" for="class_name">班级</label>
            <select id="class_name" name="class_name" class="form-select" required>
              <option value="">请选择班级</option>
              <% classOptions.forEach(function(option) { %>
                <option value="<%= option %>" <%= student.class_name === option ? 'selected' : '' %>><%= option %></option>
              <% }); %>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <label class="form-label" for="status">状态</label>
            <select id="status" name="status" class="form-select">
              <option value="在读" <%= student.status === '在读' ? 'selected' : '' %>>在读</option>
              <option value="实习" <%= student.status === '实习' ? 'selected' : '' %>>实习</option>
              <option value="休学" <%= student.status === '休学' ? 'selected' : '' %>>休学</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <label class="form-label" for="birthday">出生日期</label>
            <input id="birthday" type="date" name="birthday" class="form-control" value="<%= student.birthday ? new Date(student.birthday).toISOString().slice(0, 10) : '' %>" />
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label" for="phone">联系电话</label>
            <input id="phone" type="text" name="phone" class="form-control" value="<%= student.phone || '' %>" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label" for="email">邮箱</label>
            <input id="email" type="email" name="email" class="form-control" value="<%= student.email || '' %>" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label" for="dormitory">宿舍</label>
            <input id="dormitory" type="text" name="dormitory" class="form-control" value="<%= student.dormitory || '' %>" />
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label class="form-label" for="emergency_contact">紧急联系人</label>
            <input id="emergency_contact" type="text" name="emergency_contact" class="form-control" value="<%= student.emergency_contact || '' %>" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label class="form-label" for="emergency_phone">紧急联系电话</label>
            <input id="emergency_phone" type="text" name="emergency_phone" class="form-control" value="<%= student.emergency_phone || '' %>" />
          </div>

          <div class="col-12">
            <label class="form-label" for="notes">备注</label>
            <textarea id="notes" name="notes" class="form-control" rows="4"><%= student.notes || '' %></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><%= mode === 'create' ? '保存学生信息' : '更新学生信息' %></button>
            <a href="/students" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">取消</a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </article>

      <aside class="panel helper-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <div>
            <p class="section-kicker">Guide</p>
            <h3>录入建议</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="helper-list">
          <li>学生状态建议保持统一枚举，方便统计和后续导出。</li>
          <li>宿舍、紧急联系人和电话建议在开学初统一补录。</li>
          <li>如果学生已转入实习或休学，优先更新状态字段。</li>
          <li>班级列表来源于班级面板，新增班级后可直接在此选择。</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
